<li id="cite_note-95"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-95">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFSmith1853">Smith (1853</a>, p.&#160;107) (saying she saw the glistening metal, and estimating the breastplate's value at over 500 dollars).</span>
