<li id="cite_note-128"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-128">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFSmith1853">Smith (1853</a>, pp.&#160;115–116). Lucy may have caused the "loss" of <a href="/wiki/Lost_116_pages" title="Lost 116 pages">the 116 manuscript pages</a>, which Smith had lent her husband.</span>
