<li id="cite_note-185"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-185">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFTaves2014" class="citation journal cs1">Taves, Ann (2014). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://escholarship.org/uc/item/5s4591r8">"History and the Claims of Revelation: Joseph Smith and the Materialization of the Golden Plates"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Numen" title="Numen">Numen</a></i>. <b>61</b> (2–3): 182–207. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1163%2F15685276-12341315">10.1163/15685276-12341315</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:170900524">170900524</a> &#8211; via eScholarship.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Numen&amp;rft.atitle=History+and+the+Claims+of+Revelation%3A+Joseph+Smith+and+the+Materialization+of+the+Golden+Plates&amp;rft.volume=61&amp;rft.issue=2%E2%80%933&amp;rft.pages=182-207&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1163%2F15685276-12341315&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A170900524%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.aulast=Taves&amp;rft.aufirst=Ann&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fescholarship.org%2Fuc%2Fitem%2F5s4591r8&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AGolden+plates" class="Z3988"></span></span>
